<p><b>CARE FOR THE CAREGIVER</b>. There is still room in the
free six-week Care for the Caregiver workshop which
began on Monday, December 16. Learn what you can
do to take care of yourself as you help others in so many
ways. The group gathers on Mondays, 11:00am-1:00pm, in the Mother Cabrini Room on the lower level
